desc_long								关于这款游戏							Spheritis is a 3D race puzzle game where the player controls a ball which properties and special abilities can be changed.Explore the levels and find ways to pass the traps to reach the exit.Single player campaign:- 17 campaign levels.- 4 difficulties and one unlockable extra game mode.- Free dlc in the form of extra levels.- 8 ball types.- 7 special abilities.- 20+ Steam achievements.- Leader boards.- Steam cloud save progress.						
